definitions.definition: An instance of wallbanging; in particular a kill obtained by wallbanging.
examples: Barriers could not save them from a well-placed wallbang .

definitions.definition: A position or constellation that allows wallbanging.
examples: Careful, that wall is a wallbang .

main_definition: ( video games ) An instance of wallbanging; in particular a kill obtained by wallbanging.
secondary_definitions: ( video games ) A position or constellation that allows wallbanging.
